description:
Garage Sale Mystery: Guilty Until Proven Innocent



Jennifer Shannon's old friend from college, Sandra, has an antiques store that is closing and she's ecstatic to get first pick on all the goodies. She expects to find a few exquisite pieces but she doesn't expect to find a dead body. To make matters worse, Sandra is arrested for murder. Jennifer has no choice but to get involved and find the real killer to prove her friend's innocence.
